connect20/sniip_retailer_connect.name: connect20/Sniip_Retailer_Connect

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/sniip_retailer_connect.description: This module allows you to sync your Magento Retail store to the Sniip marketplace, allowing shoppers to browse and shop on your store within a native app experience.
